---
title: Creamy Chicken and Pea Puff Pastry Pie with Wholegrain Mustard and Mashed Potatoes
description: Pies are comforting and perfect for winter, plus this chicken pie is real comfort food. Here, we're using mustard to flavour the creamy sauce with chicken and peas for a delicious and hearty meal.
